* Carnage watched Cyber Claw drop into the waters below her and Teltoli, she 
sighed and looked back at the Fuzor. They were now flying over the shore and 
it was time that she relieved the bot of her heavy load, she looked down at 
the sand and sighed...she let go.
Carnage absorbed the impact of her drop with the muscles of her legs and 
tail, she then looked back up at the flying Fuzor...big drop!
She sighed and looked at the ground beneath her feet, it was a wonderful 
sight!
Carnage then looked back towards the swimming clone and sighed again...*

" Come on, we only have a few clicks to cover before we reach the Maximals."

* It was then that she continued her journey to get Teltoli to a home that 
she could be somewhat safe in.
Carnage snarled, and soon after that she would have to track down Megs and 
kill him, but that one question continued to bother her...what would she do 
after that?*
